{"type":"message","id":"fcc28567","parentId":"1addf213","timestamp":"2026-04-25T03:52:55.847Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. If runtime-provided startup context is included for this first turn, use it before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Saturday, April 25th, 2026 - 11:52 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-25 03:52 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777089175768}}
