{"type":"message","id":"a85e1574","parentId":"b9a6d975","timestamp":"2026-04-25T04:29:34.443Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经继续写进 `HEARTBEAT.md` 了。\n\n这次补进去的是两块关键判断：\n\n- **什么内容值得深读**\n- **什么内容默认跳过**\n\n现在这份 heartbeat 说明已经从“会学习”升级成“会筛选、会深读、会克制”，更适合你现在这套长期运行流。\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步还能继续帮你补最后一层：  \n**把 heartbeat 输出推荐时的固定格式也压成一个小模板**，这样以后推送会更稳、更像一个成熟的主动学习助手。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f6707160cd42800169ec432b722c8190ae7d64834810e965\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":58995,"output":133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59128,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777091367465,"responseId":"resp_06f6707160cd42800169ec432951b88190b4306c02c7a9c818"}}
