{"type":"message","id":"202a829e","parentId":"3b6e1b0b","timestamp":"2026-04-25T04:32:57.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经把推荐输出模板也写进 `HEARTBEAT.md` 了。\n\n现在这套 clawCast 心跳学习流已经补齐了 4 层：\n\n- **先筛选**\n- **再判定是否深读**\n- **必要时抓正文**\n- **最后按固定格式输出推荐**\n\n这样以后 heartbeat 更像一个稳定的主动学习系统，而不是随机推送器。\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以再帮你做一个很实用的收尾：  \n**把这份 HEARTBEAT.md 再压缩成“更短但不丢关键规则”的版本**，减少以后每次 heartbeat 的上下文负担。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f6707160cd42800169ec43f54f10819099ee46c2eb3b5d4b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":62017,"output":148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62165,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777091568775,"responseId":"resp_06f6707160cd42800169ec43f293008190970aa7d2b87fba81"}}
