{"type":"message","id":"3b71e200","parentId":"8817812e","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:03:53.702Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_BRV6krzGLG6TYFwTO9QoHVLt|fc_06f6707160cd42800169ec7568d008819090bb2da3890f0e30","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":220,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install/README.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":220,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install/README.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":124770,"output":48,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777104227065,"responseId":"resp_06f6707160cd42800169ec7564ae38819089f7db98d33df039"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a4e845c","parentId":"3b71e200","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:03:53.836Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_BRV6krzGLG6TYFwTO9QoHVLt|fc_06f6707160cd42800169ec7568d008819090bb2da3890f0e30","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# sub2api-gpt-image\n\n给 OpenClaw 用的一个轻量 skill 模板，适用于通过 CLIProxyAPI / sub2api 这类 OpenAI 兼容网关调用 `POST /v1/responses`，并强制启用 `image_generation` 工具来生图。\n\n## 你的环境\n\n- Base URL: `http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1`\n- 平台: Linux\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```text\nsub2api-gpt-image-install/\n├── README.md\n├── SKILL.md\n├── EXTEND.example.md\n└── scripts/\n    └── generate-image.sh\n```\n\n## 安装方法\n\n把整个目录复制到：\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image\ncp -r /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/sub2api-gpt-image-install/* ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/\nchmod +x ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh\n```\n\n## 你需要做的配置\n\n复制一份示例配置：\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image\ncp ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/EXTEND.example.md ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/EXTEND.md\n```\n\n然后填写：\n- `base_url`\n- `api_key`\n- 默认模型别名\n- 默认输出目录\n\n## 直接调用示例\n\n```bash\nbash ~/.openclaw/skills/sub2api-gpt-image/scripts/generate-image.sh \\\n  --base-url 'http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1' \\\n  --api-key '你的CLIProxyAPI密钥' \\\n  --model 'gpt-image-1024x1024' \\\n  --prompt '画一张赛博朋克香港夜景，要有中文招牌，电影感' \\\n  --output '/tmp/cyberpunk-hk.png'\n```\n\n## 说明\n\n这个脚本依赖：\n- `curl`\n- `jq`\n- `base64`\n\n如果响应里包含 `image_generation_call.result`，脚本会自动解码并保存成图片。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777104233772}}
{"type":"message","id":"75daa91d","parentId":"7a4e845c","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:04:01.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_YpEtJ89pJJTDWub0KJk2DbQy|fc_06f6707160cd42800169ec757111f8819085f46d4440fc4774","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":220,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/debug_cliproxy_image.py"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":220,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/debug_cliproxy_image.py\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":125317,"output":44,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125361,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777104233842,"responseId":"resp_06f6707160cd42800169ec756bf5ec81909bc656b1570201dd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5071fda9","parentId":"75daa91d","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:04:02.069Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_YpEtJ89pJJTDWub0KJk2DbQy|fc_06f6707160cd42800169ec757111f8819085f46d4440fc4774","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport json\nfrom urllib.request import Request, urlopen\nfrom urllib.error import HTTPError, URLError\n\napi_url = 'http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses'\napi_key = '[REDACTED]'\nbody = {\n    'model': 'gpt-image-1536x1024',\n    'instructions': 'You are a helpful assistant.',\n    'input': [{\n        'type': 'message',\n        'role': 'user',\n        'content': [{'type': 'input_text', 'text': '画一张赛博朋克夜景，要有霓虹灯和中文招牌'}]\n    }],\n    'parallel_tool_calls': True,\n    'stream': False,\n    'store': False,\n}\n\ndata = json.dumps(body).encode('utf-8')\nreq = Request(api_url, data=data, headers={\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n    'Authorization': f'Bearer {api_key}',\n}, method='POST')\n\ntry:\n    with urlopen(req) as resp:\n        print(resp.status)\n        print(resp.read().decode('utf-8'))\nexcept HTTPError as e:\n    print('HTTP_ERROR', e.code)\n    print(e.read().decode('utf-8', errors='replace'))\nexcept URLError as e:\n    print('URL_ERROR', e)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777104242005}}
