{"type":"message","id":"22150166","parentId":"55339af5","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:04:20.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经继续往下排了，进展是有的：\n\n## 已确认的事实\n你这个图像编辑链路背后**不是本机 8317 服务**，而是有现成的远程 API 可用：\n\n- 远程地址：`http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses`\n- 我刚实际探测到了，它会正常返回：\n  - `401 Unauthorized`\n  - `Missing API key`\n\n这说明：\n\n- 服务本身 **活着**\n- 网络是通的\n- 路由没问题\n- 之前失败的原因是本地 `.env` 写成了 `127.0.0.1:8317`\n\n## 当前结论\n问题已经从：\n\n- “API 没启动”\n\n变成了：\n\n- **API 地址配错了**\n\n也就是说现在最可能的修法就是：\n\n把 `gpt-image-generator` 的 `.env` 里的\n\n```env\nPY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8317/v1/responses\n```\n\n改成\n\n```env\nPY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL=http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses\n```\n\n## 下一步\n如果你同意，我现在就直接帮你改这个配置，然后重新跑那张结婚登记照编辑。\n\n你回我一句：\n\n**同意改配置**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f6707160cd42800169ec757ee9e48190bcff03a2189af3f6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":125835,"output":299,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126134,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777104249330,"responseId":"resp_06f6707160cd42800169ec757b3f7c8190a50ef03a4e8ef8da"}}
