{"type":"message","id":"ea049911","parentId":"622924eb","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:04:48.155Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经直接替你换成这个远程 API 了，现在马上重跑编辑。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f6707160cd42800169ec759908688190a4e54b248be364d0\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_NiLmDs64S2nw38EiRI9rWEjK|fc_06f6707160cd42800169ec75995b9481908bc96c8c0b679bc7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image_edit.py --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/ce86c855-360e-4d9e-ae99-75344acea5c7.jpg --prompt 'Edit this photo into a formal Chinese marriage registration portrait while preserving the original facial features of both people. Two-inch ID-photo style, 3:2 aspect ratio, half-body framing from above chest to top of head. Solid deep red background (#8B0000), clean and even. Woman on the left and slightly in front, man on the right slightly behind, both outer shoulders nearly aligned. Eye-level front-facing shot, soft even frontal lighting, no harsh shadows. The woman has elegant long black hair past the chest with slight volume, forehead, eyebrows and both ears visible, one side of long hair in front. She wears a sleeveless white French light-luxury satin dress, pearl drop earrings, natural refined makeup, natural toothy smile showing about 8 teeth. The man has neat black side-parted short hair, clean-shaven, natural toothy smile, wearing a dark navy-black double-breasted suit, white shirt, and navy tie with small light or gold dots. Overall style formal, elegant, warm, classic marriage registration photo. Keep identity highly consistent with the source image.' --out-base /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/marriage-registration-photo","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","timeout":1800,"yieldMs":1000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python