{"type":"message","id":"91bb1222","parentId":"1bc99da7","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:40:26.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我先直接帮你测了 `gpt-image-2`。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f6707160cd42800169ec7df57a088190a7899884a08cb22e\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"测出来了，结果很关键：\n\n## `gpt-image-2` 不能走 `/v1/responses`\n服务端明确返回：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"model gpt-image-2 is only supported on /v1/images/generations and /v1/images/edits\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 这说明什么\n这个网关对 `gpt-image-2` 的要求是：\n\n- **生图** 走 `/v1/images/generations`\n- **改图** 走 `/v1/images/edits`\n\n而不是 `/v1/responses`\n\n## 结论\n这其实是个进展。  \n因为我们现在终于知道：\n\n- 这个网关不是完全按 responses 工具调用那套来\n- 它对 `gpt-image-2` 明确要求走 **images API 路线**\n\n## 下一步最合理\n如果你同意，我现在就直接继续替你测试：\n\n1. `/v1/images/generations` 能不能成功生图  \n2. 如果生图能通，再试 `/v1/images/edits` 能不能改你那张登记照\n\n这一步比之前瞎撞靠谱多了。  \n你回我一句：\n\n**继续测 images API**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f6707160cd42800169ec7df5bb908190a91096d9549a42ae\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":135427,"output":301,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135728,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777106416783,"responseId":"resp_06f6707160cd42800169ec7df28d44819090f81c4023a44628"}}
