{"type":"message","id":"6687bea6","parentId":"8b095cc2","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:41:46.079Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Tp2PKqiHCML9zkt1qFREvAgR|fc_06f6707160cd42800169ec7e48654c8190aa97cd969ec268aa","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== /images/generations HTTP_ERROR 400\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"Tool choice 'image_generation' not found in 'tools' parameter.\",\n    \"type\": \"invalid_request_error\",\n    \"param\": \"tool_choice\",\n    \"code\": null\n  }\n}\n=== /images/edits HTTP_ERROR 400\n{\"error\":{\"message\":\"Invalid request: images[].image_url is required (file_id is not supported)\",\"type\":\"invalid_request_error\"}}\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"swift-shoal","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"=== /images/generations HTTP_ERROR 400\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"message\": \"Tool choice 'image_generation' not found in 'tools' parameter.\",\n    \"type\": \"invalid_request_error\",\n    \"param\": \"tool_choice\",\n    \"code\": null\n  }\n}\n=== /images/edits HTTP_ERROR 400\n{\"error\":{\"message\":\"Invalid request: images[].image_url is required (file_id is not supported)\",\"type\":\"invalid_request_error\"}}\n","name":"python3 <<'PY'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777106506015}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf689516","parentId":"6687bea6","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:41:58.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我测完了，这个网关的行为现在更清楚了：\n\n## 结果 1，`/images/generations`\n它居然还是返回：\n\n```json\nTool choice 'image_generation' not found in 'tools' parameter.\n```\n\n这很反常，说明它的 `/images/generations` 也不是标准 OpenAI Images API 行为，明显做了自定义兼容。\n\n## 结果 2，`/images/edits`\n它返回的是：\n\n```json\nInvalid request: images[].image_url is required (file_id is not supported)\n```\n\n这个信息反而很有价值，说明：\n\n- 这条编辑接口**确实存在**\n- 它不接受标准文件上传方式\n- 它要求的是：\n\n**`images[].image_url`**\n\n也就是要传一个**图片 URL**，而不是本地文件或 `file_id`\n\n---\n\n## 现在我们已经知道的关键点\n这个网关大概率要求：\n\n- 不是标准 OpenAI Responses 工具流\n- 也不是标准 OpenAI Images 上传文件流\n- 它更像一个自定义接口，尤其编辑时要求：\n\n### `images: [{ image_url: \"...\" }]`\n\n## 下一步最靠谱\n如果你还要继续打通“原图改登记照”这条线，我建议现在就做这一步：\n\n1. 先把你那张原图放成一个可访问的 URL\n2. 再按它要求的 `images[].image_url` 格式去打 `/v1/images/edits`\n\n这个方向现在比前面所有尝试都更接近正确答案。\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步就继续帮你构造这个 **image_url 版 edits 请求**。  \n你回我一句：\n\n**继续试 image_url**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f6707160cd42800169ec7e4fbcb08190993b49493f50ac28\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":136393,"output":388,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136781,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777106506087,"responseId":"resp_06f6707160cd42800169ec7e4c20248190b953e317036ba540"}}
