{"type":"message","id":"c85a076f","parentId":"911b0237","timestamp":"2026-04-25T08:42:11.814Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经把 `images API` 这条线也测完了，结果很有信息量：\n\n### `/v1/images/generations`\n返回还是：\n\n```json\nTool choice 'image_generation' not found in 'tools' parameter.\n```\n\n这说明这个网关的 `generations` 也不是标准 OpenAI 行为，明显带了自定义兼容逻辑。\n\n### `/v1/images/edits`\n返回的是：\n\n```json\nInvalid request: images[].image_url is required (file_id is not supported)\n```\n\n这个更关键，说明：\n\n- 编辑接口是存在的\n- 但它**不接受标准文件上传**\n- 它要求传的是 **`images[].image_url`**\n\n也就是说，现在最接近打通的方向已经出现了：\n\n**把原图变成一个可访问的 URL，再按 `image_url` 格式打 `/v1/images/edits`。**\n\n如果你还要继续，我下一步就该往这条线上试。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f6707160cd42800169ec7e6036408190949abf2571930afa\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":136893,"output":217,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137110,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777106523300,"responseId":"resp_06f6707160cd42800169ec7e5d60b4819090ed5551b8188654"}}
